NUMBER 1407
NAME Ysarda, The Ornery Pig
REGION 6
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 82
*DESCRIPTION_START
This rundown bar seems to be a haven to some of the ugliest and sleaziest
creatures you've ever seen. A large bar sits along the back wall, tended
by a young male human who seems out of place, being so cleanshaven. Nearly
two dozen tables litter the sprawling room, many with chairs standing upright
next to them, but just as many are laying on the ground in varying states of
repair. A haze fills the air, as several of the more animated patrons smoke
heavily, while a few more patrons with watchful eyes sit quietly at corner
tables. A sizable green lizard lounges across the bar, looking around sadly,
occasionally taking a puff on a cigarette.
*DESCRIPTION_END
