STOREITEM 241 522 5 ; CHAMPAGNE
STOREITEM 1561 800 5 ; WHISKEY
STOREITEM 1562 959 3 ; BEER
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
The bar runs along the entire back of the wall, made of what was once most
likely a very sturdy wood. It's now rundown, cracks along it in several
places, and generally falling apart.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 7
You check out the fine selection here at the Ornery Pig.

Red Wine        1 kentaurs
White Wine      1 kentaurs
Murg Ale        2 kentaurs (Andoran import)
Dragonslayer
Champagne       5 kentaurs (specialty import)
Nocturpede
Whiskey         5 kentaurs (specialty import)
Potent Beer     3 kentaurs (house specialty)
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB GO 4
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR ORG = 21
      ECHO PLAYER You ascend down a hidden stairway without anyone noticing.
      MOVEGROUP 1406
   ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER You start to make your way down a dark and dirty staircase, but the bartender yells, "Hey now! Don't be thinking of raiding my wine cellar!"
      ECHO OTHERS %N starts to go down dark and dirty staircase, but the bartender yells, "Hey now! Don't be thinking of raiding my wine cellar!"
   ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CLIMB 4
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR ORG = 21
      ECHO PLAYER You ascend down a hidden stairway without anyone noticing.
      MOVEGROUP 1406
   ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER You start to make your way down a dark and dirty staircase, but the bartender yells, "Hey now! Don't be thinking of raiding my wine cellar!"
      ECHO OTHERS %N starts to go down dark and dirty staircase, but the bartender yells, "Hey now! Don't be thinking of raiding my wine cellar!"
   ENDIF
ENDIF
