NUMBER 1406
NAME Ysarda, The Masquerade
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 82
*DESCRIPTION_START
The room is done up quite simply. The walls are painted a deep midnight black,
causing the illusion of empty space. Along the western wall, several dozen
pure white alzyron masks seem to hang in midair, their empty eyes gazing
ahead. A long table sits in the center of the room with several comfortable
chairs lined up along it. A bound leather book sits closed on the table.
*DESCRIPTION_END
